<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd" []>
<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="find-replace" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Find&amp;Replace</title>
  <conbody id="body">
    <p id="find-replace-intro">Serna lets you quickly <xref href="find.xml">find</xref> or <xref href="find-replace.xml">find&amp;replace</xref> any text that occurs either in the content of a  document  or  a comment, or in the name of an attribute or its value. You can also <xref href="search-by-using-xslt-match-patterns.xml">search for elements that satisfy specific conditions</xref>.</p>
    <p>You can do the following find&amp;replace<indexterm>find&amp;replace</indexterm> operations:<ul>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="find.xml">
              <b>Find</b>
            </xref>.</p>
          <p conref="find.xml#find/find-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="search-by-using-xslt-match-patterns.xml">
              <b>Search by using an XSLT match pattern</b>
            </xref>.</p>
          <p conref="search-by-using-xslt-match-patterns.xml#search-by-using-xslt-match-patterns/search-by-using-xslt-match-pattern-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="replace.xml">
              <b>Replace</b>
            </xref>. </p>
          <p conref="replace.xml#replace/replace-intro"/>
        </li>
      </ul><note>
        <p>These find&amp;replace operations can also be performed <xref href="find-replace-with-docked-find-replace-dialog.xml">through the docked Find and Replace Dialog</xref>.</p>
      </note></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
